# OpenAI Model Parameters

## GPT-5.x models require `max_completion_tokens`

GPT-5.4, GPT-5.4-mini, and all GPT-5.x models do **NOT** support `max_tokens`. Use `max_completion_tokens` instead.

```typescript
// ❌ BAD — will return 400 "Unsupported parameter"
body: JSON.stringify({
  model: 'gpt-5.4-mini',
  max_tokens: 1024,
})

// ✅ GOOD
body: JSON.stringify({
  model: 'gpt-5.4-mini',
  max_completion_tokens: 1024,
})
```

## Snacky model constants

| Constant | Model | Use case |
|---|---|---|
| `MODEL_SIMPLE` | `gpt-5.4-mini` | Intent classification, translations, lightweight tasks |
| `MODEL_COMPLEX` | `gpt-5.4` | Meal suggestions, plan creation, health insights |
